---
By: Sathya Sai Baba
Locus:
  Page: 467
  Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Teacher
---
The Guru (teacher) is the person who discovers that you have fallen into a
wrong road that leads into further and further darkness. For he knows the
right road and he is full of love for all who strive to escape the travails
of the night, without lamps to light their steps.
